Pattern Recognition
Tree + DFS + Bottom-Up Computation

Interview Insight
This is a classic: Top-Down → Bottom-Up Optimization
Brute Force: Check balance
Then compute heights repeatedly.
Optimal: Compute heights while checking balance.
The -1 trick is a very common interview pattern for propagating failure information upward during DFS. 
